title: Nicki Minaj releases two new tracks!!! But is it good????
itunes:title: Nicki Minaj releases two new tracks!!! But is it good????
description:
4-13 Friday- Today on the Breakfast Club, the crew played two brand new songs from Nicki Minaj and gave listeners the mic to voice their opinion on her music. They also discussed Nicki's recent comments in which she expressed disappointment in Cardi B and Quavo following the release of Motorsport, Meek Mill's incarceration and his beef with Drake. Charlamagne gave his Donkey of the Day to an individual who represents the "crazy" state of Florida. Plus, comedian Andrew Schulz of the Brilliant Idiots podcast stopped by to talk about his brother taking a swing at his co-host Charlamagne, pregnancy sex, over-sensitivity and more.
